{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ke83YqTbEscENUcVsEGNkV","type":"tool_result","content":"345\tTaskRef     ← \"T-\" Digit+                         ; the bare form used to reference another task\n346\tTag         ← FlagTag / ActionTag                 ; leading position only (§4.3)\n347\tFlagTag     ← \"[\" (\"USER\" / \"BATCH\") \"]\" WS\n348\tActionTag   ← \"[AUTO:\" Word \"]\" WS Text?          ; args are remainder of text\n349\tAnnot       ← WS \"[\" Key \":\" WS Value \"]\"         ; e.g. [feat: \"...\"], [fix: \"...\"]\n350\tDepsLine    ← Indent* \"@deps\" (WS TaskRef)+ NL    ; bare IDs, no trailing colon\n351\tRuledOut    ← Indent* \"[RULEDOUT]\" WS Text NL\n352\tIndent      ← (WS WS)+                            ; numeric nesting, 2-space canonical\n353\tProse       ← (! Item ! PhaseHead ! Subsection . )* NL\n354\t```\n355\t\n356\tNotes on the grammar:\n357\t\n358\t- Indentation is significant for nesting but **numeric**, not fixed.\n359\t  A child task requires strictly greater indent than its parent."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7daf3165-203a-4a0a-9a4a-c7b8a0f7e266","uuid":"63296686-c52b-4982-b02d-4217ba19e05f","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:02:19.544Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/mhcoen/proj/bob/design/planfile.md","content":"TaskRef     ← \"T-\" Digit+                         ; the bare form used to reference another task\nTag         ← FlagTag / ActionTag                 ; leading position only (§4.3)\nFlagTag     ← \"[\" (\"USER\" / \"BATCH\") \"]\" WS\nActionTag   ← \"[AUTO:\" Word \"]\" WS Text?          ; args are remainder of text\nAnnot       ← WS \"[\" Key \":\" WS Value \"]\"         ; e.g. [feat: \"...\"], [fix: \"...\"]\nDepsLine    ← Indent* \"@deps\" (WS TaskRef)+ NL    ; bare IDs, no trailing colon\nRuledOut    ← Indent* \"[RULEDOUT]\" WS Text NL\nIndent      ← (WS WS)+                            ; numeric nesting, 2-space canonical\nProse       ← (! Item ! PhaseHead ! Subsection . )* NL\n```\n\nNotes on the grammar:\n\n- Indentation is significant for nesting but **numeric**, not fixed.\n  A child task requires strictly greater indent than its parent.","numLines":15,"startLine":345,"totalLines":755}}}
